                <note rend="inline" type="source">119.2/6–1549: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-06-24T18:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 24, 1949—6 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>741. Ur 1289 June 15. Dept files contain no info re China network origin in
                    addition that supplied by Off Emb Canton in tel 405 June 17, rptd Dept Cantel
                    605.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
